        "product_description": {
            "value": "Repair your neoprene wetsuits, gloves, and waders with the GEAR AID Wetsuit Repair Kit. This heat-activated Tenacious Tape Neoprene Patch fixes tears permanently using just a household iron. The black 10\"x6\" fabric patch can be cut to size to repair tears or reinforce high-wear areas like elbows and knees that require lasting flexibility and durability. It's also compatible with stretch fabrics such as spandex and Lycra. The complete kit includes the Iron-On Neoprene Patch along with Aquaseal NEO Contact Cement (1.5 fl oz), which repairs torn or ripped neoprene permanently in just 30 minutes. Aquaseal NEO cures to a flexible black rubber and bonds to latex, making it ideal for a wide range of gear repairs. Whether you're patching a small tear or reinforcing a stress point, this versatile kit keeps your gear in top condition for your next adventure in the water. Packaging may vary.",
